                </svg></a>
            <a href="/cadastroClientes" class="text text-info">Cadastro Cliente<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-journal" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
